{"tid":2450433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：阿拉斯加會談前拿香港議題出來 美國是要反檯嗎 ?","createTime":"2021-03-17T11:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T15:52:50.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2462d34def0e2f980074afaebc8e66090b7b34a3","tid":2450433,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"環球時報：若美國政府實施新一輪制裁 中方必以牙還牙<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院公布《香港自治法》報告的更新內容，列出24名中港官員，國務卿布林肯指他們的行為削弱了香港的自治。<br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》發表社評認為，這樣的制裁威脅，對那些中國官員不可能產生任何影響。如果美國這屆政府實施新一輪制裁，中方必將再一次以牙還牙。<br />\n<br />\n社評認為，美方的做法都是想要製造在阿拉斯加壓向中國對話者的聲勢，為對話設置議題，但這種表演與中美對話的基本意義背道而馳。既然對話，就要找些共同點出來，否則隔空施壓就夠。社評認為，中國人只要去對話，就會禮貌為先。但在香港、台灣以及南海等問題上，中國的立場、道義以及實力是高度匹配，有充裕的能力以不變應萬變，既不咄咄逼人，也不逆來順受。所以，一個美方發指示、中方接指示的阿拉斯加對話決不會發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581107-20210317.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581107-20210317.htm&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=f763902f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581107-20210317.htm&h=c60482a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581107-20210317.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8a9170ac66b94172e8541408aa6b2894db7e46ca","tid":2450433,"uid":284038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"環球時報&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b947bb41a6604142adc48342c493cdb7f4e30fb0","tid":2450433,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有美國人冇得去中國啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好慘慘豬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c0a9a6a9b5c658296ae92ac7ea4c1e3cad605a","tid":2450433,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你敢嗎？支那狗"},{"pid":"24af1f461f629dc58ca2dd8dcd30fe757df5ffc4","tid":2450433,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"制裁冇影響既話點解仲要以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39125a364e4631b48a1e6715eacdd4d979c5c191","tid":2450433,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"點還牙 唔比幻幻敗登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca306a642f9fab597d8d750b024f67ffbecf32c","tid":2450433,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"這樣的制裁威脅，對那些中國官員<span class=\"red\">不可能產生任何影響</span>。如果美國這屆政府實施新一輪制裁，中方必將再一次<span class=\"red\">以牙還牙</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國意思係<br />\n我唯有諗啲同樣冇影響力嘅反制啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6100d182c6e987c85d7279b65a92ace10f3d7e","tid":2450433,"uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:59:59.000Z","msg":"以牙還牙 = 搞鳩香港人"},{"pid":"daa270a3a59ef3dc1b51a714acfeb35e20a4ebf5","tid":2450433,"